Hello,
 

​​​​​We hope you were able to attend the Public Sector Data Summit last week. If you did attend, we really hope that you enjoyed the event as much as we did. 
 

For your convenience, we have included links to some of the resources that were available on the day, and invite you to visit them in your own time:

  • learn more about our Big Data and Analytics agreement and understand how we can support the creation of intelligent data and analytics functions
  • join our upcoming webinar on Tuesday 7 February where we will provide an introduction of our new Mobile Voice and Data Services agreement
  • ​​​explore our technology solutions webpage to download our whitepapers and on-demand webinar

We have also included the slideshow that Philip Orumwense, Commercial Director and Chief Procurement Officer Technology, presented during his keynote speaker session, where he discussed driving efficiencies across the Public Sector.
